  "text": "Biotinylated NAD ϩ and the TACS-Saphire substrate were purchased from Trevigen. Streptavidin-peroxidase was from Sigma (St Louis, MO). Peroxynitrite was from Cayman Chemical (Ann Arbor, MI). The PARP inhibitor PJ-34 was synthesized in our laboratory as described [CITATION_1] . Cryoembedding medium was from Shandon (Pittsburgh, PA). Nuclear fast Red and Vectamount were obtained from Vector Laboratories (Burlingame, CA). Triti-ated NAD was from NEN Life Science Products (Boston, MA). All other chemicals were from Sigma.",
